For the first public release:

[X] Split OSA.app() in OSA.app_with_name(), OSA.app_with_bundle_id(), 
    OSA.app_with_signature(), OSA.app_with_path and implement them.
[X] Add elements write support.
[X] Rewrite the sdef parser using native libxml2 code.
[X] Allow the possibility to set a timeout for an AppleEvent.
[X] Allow the possibility to desactivate the lazy AppleEvent sends.
[X] Add a tool to generate RDoc documentation.

Further releases:

